Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.53,0:25:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,月火Da☆Yo！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.61,0:25:12.44,NoteV,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\pos(1512,198)}月火DaYo！
