Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.84,0:25:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,转眼间物语系列第二季也要迎来总数第二十话了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.36,0:25:23.29,NoteV,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\pos(237,276)}黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.36,0:25:23.29,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\pos(1320,177)}出现了一个好厉害的东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.36,0:25:23.29,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\pos(1098,342)}连我也
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.36,0:25:23.29,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\pos(1599,342)}拿它没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.33,0:25:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,干脆一口气播个四十话算了！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.30,0:25:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就要追上原作了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.34,0:25:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋  这时候就轮到我们Fire Sisters的外传登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.29,0:25:32.17,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\pos(969,183)}哎？你知道镇住这个的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.29,0:25:32.17,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\pos(1536,765)}我什么都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.21,0:25:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,预告篇Quiz！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.21,0:25:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiz！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.10,0:25:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,说起圣诞节就是12月25日
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.69,0:25:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,的确是25日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.82,0:25:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,另外圣诞{\shad3\4a&H00&\blur2\fs80}树{\fs\blur\4a\shad}节可是12月7日哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.82,0:25:33.50,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(854,980)}Tree
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.17,0:25:41.01,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\pos(1398,189)}镇内少女选美大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.17,0:25:41.01,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\pos(987,786)}就用这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.50,0:25:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.30,0:25:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕从圣诞树节开始到圣诞节的18天里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.61,0:25:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在忙着装饰圣诞树吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.05,0:25:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是费工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.01,0:25:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来就是Quiz了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.06,0:25:49.94,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\pos(918,153)}一齐出现  一齐出现
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.06,0:25:49.94,NoteV,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\pos(294,312)}吾有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.06,0:25:49.94,NoteV,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\pos(1656,312)}亮相！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.06,0:25:49.94,Note,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\pos(993,861)}这能行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.60,0:25:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,雏祭是3月3日
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.86,0:25:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么雏{\shad3\4a&H00&\blur2\fs80}祭{\fs\blur\4a\shad}是哪一天呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.86,0:25:47.36,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(874,980)}Tree
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.54,0:25:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,3月7日吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.97,0:25:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还是3月3日
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.65,0:25:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  鬼物语  第四话
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.72,0:25:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,忍与时间  其四
